# Test Chat API Endpoints (No Auth Required)

### Get all chat rooms (for a quick overview)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/test/chat/rooms/all
Accept: application/json

### Get chat rooms for a specific user
GET http://localhost:8000/api/test/chat/rooms?user_id=1
Accept: application/json

### Get messages for a specific chat room
GET http://localhost:8000/api/test/chat/rooms/1/messages?user_id=1
Accept: application/json

### Send a message in a chat room
POST http://localhost:8000/api/test/chat/rooms/1/messages
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "user_id": 1,
    "content": "This is a test message"
}

### Get messages with pagination
GET http://localhost:8000/api/test/chat/rooms/1/messages?user_id=1&limit=10
Accept: application/json

### Get messages before a specific message ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/test/chat/rooms/1/messages?user_id=1&limit=10&before_id=20
Accept: application/json
